u kenna conned. if u wanna claim waiting time1. reach pickup point Live chat CS tell them u wanna claim waiting time for order number xxx (or your current order if u only have one on hand). They will put in their remarks and close chat2. pickup liao contact Live Chat CS again  say claim xx min. must say at least 10 min for the min $2 cos first 10 min is the grace period for the sender to pass u the stuff.3. they will end chat. Cancel your current order  and reissue u a new order inclusive of the waiting time. One thing to note is to ensure that the Gross amount is add $2/$4/$6 to the older order.So far if i reach early and i need to wait  i don't claim. cos i early ma. so if both sender early and rider early then shiok
